  "instructions": [
    "heat coconut oil in a pressure cooker over medium heat.",
    "add onion, garlic, and ginger and saut\u00159 until softened.",
    "add chinese broccoli and kale and saut\u00159 for 2 minutes.",
    "add chili flakes, soy sauce, rice vinegar, salt, and black pepper and stir to combine.",
    "close pressure cooker and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "release pressure and stir in toasted sesame seeds.",
    "serve hot and enjoy!"
